🏅Grooming position available 🏅

&nbsp;

Plain Bay Farm is in search of a show jumping groom to join our team! We have 2 positions available. Due to shared housing, we are looking for a female groom at this time. We are a sales and training operation based out of Wellington FL, Middleburg VA, and Nancy France. This is a full time position that includes salary, housing, per diem, and client tips at horse shows. Each groom will be responsible for their assigned horses. We are willing to train. We are looking for a motivated team player to join our operation with great horses and great clients. This is a grooming position only, no riding available.

Noble Road Equestrian is adding to their team. Are you passionate about horses and love teaching? We have a exciting opportunity for you! We are looking for!

*Experience at teaching beginning to intermediate riders

*Competition experience

*A love for kids

*Upbeat, energetic personality

*Teaching a curriculum based program

&nbsp;

Competitive pay, Ideal schedule, Part- time, Dressage, western and horsemanship disciplines. Beautiful facility

